# 1️⃣2️⃣ INVOICE APPROVAL WORKFLOW

Depending on value:

* Auto-approval (low-risk)
* Manager approval
* Finance review
* Multi-level approval (Logic 11)

All approval actions digitally signed (Logic 13).

