# 1️⃣3️⃣ ACCOUNTING SYSTEM INTEGRATION

Logic 19 exports structured data to:

* ERP systems
* General ledger
* Accounts payable module
* Cost center records
* Project accounting

Ensures real-time financial reconciliation.

---

# 1️⃣4️⃣ DOCUMENT IMMUTABILITY and ARCHIVING

After approval:

* Invoice locked
* Version history frozen
* Stored in secure archive
* Retention policy applied

Retention may follow regulatory standards (e.g., 5–10 years).

---

# 1️⃣5️⃣ EXCEPTION HANDLING WORKFLOW

If mismatch detected:

```
Invoice Flagged
    ↓
Exception Ticket Created
    ↓
Assigned to Review Officer
    ↓
Supplier Notified (if needed)
    ↓
Resolution Logged
```

Resolutions may include:

* Adjustment
* Credit note
* Rejection
* Re-submission

All steps auditable.

---

# 1️⃣6️⃣ CREDIT NOTE and ADJUSTMENT LOGIC

System supports:

* Partial invoice approval
* Credit note issuance
* Refund tracking
* Adjustment linking to original invoice

Maintains financial traceability.

